name: Eric Phillips
text: Great vacation rental for the family or families. 3 flrs, elevator, pool, 2 slip boathouse w/ quick access to the bay & Gulf.

name: Stephanie Melton
text: Good neighborhood to bring a boat.  Close to white sandy beaches.  Good shopping and restaurants close by.

name: Jenny Mann
text: Best experience !!  Very clean. Highly Recommend !!
